src/
│
├── main.jsx
├── App.jsx
├── Global.css
│
├── assets/               # images, logos, icons
├── components/           # reusable UI components (e.g. Button, Card)
├── features/             # actual features of your app
│   ├── settings/
│   └── users/
│
├── pages/                # top-level route pages
│   ├── Home.jsx
│   ├── About.jsx
│   ├── SignIn.jsx
│   └── SignUp.jsx
│
├── hooks/                # custom hooks like useAuth
├── utils/                # helper functions
├── services/             # API logic (e.g. authService.js, api.js)
└── routes/               # Optional: central route config or ProtectedRoute.jsx


src/
├── hooks/
│   ├── useAuth.js
│   └── useDebounce.js
│
├── utils/
│   ├── formatCurrency.js
│   └── capitalize.js


| Folder      | Purpose                                                             | Example Logic                        |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `utils/`    | Generic **helper functions** — pure, stateless                      | formatDate, capitalize, debounce     |
| `services/` | Logic that interacts with **external systems** (API, auth, storage) | loginUser, fetchProducts, uploadFile |

| Syntax       | Type             | Can embed variables? | Example                |
| ------------ | ---------------- | -------------------- | ---------------------- |
| `'text'`     | String literal   | ❌ No                 | `'Hello, ' + name`     |
| `"text"`     | String literal   | ❌ No                 | `"Age: " + age`        |
| `` `text` `` | Template literal | ✅ Yes                | `` `Hello, ${name}` `` |
